==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Optogram
<hw>Op"to*gram</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Opt</ets>ic +
<ets>-gram</ets>: cf. F. <ets>optogramme</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>An image of external objects fixed on the
retina by the photochemical action of light on the visual purple. See
<er>Optography</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Optography</ent>⟦br⟧
